data.title: How can one create a great YouTube page?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 4): At my last job we had an outsized financial return on a not to big subscriber base. There were two reasons: we had content on YouTube in a high demand vertical. But more important the content we had was excellent.

There's only so much room for latitude in the YouTube templates. ...
